                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <span class="maxproduct"><img src="~/images/product1-1.jpg" width="400px" alt=""></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-details">
                                <a href="#">
                                    <h1>Khóa học @item.Ten</h1>
